                        Miru[m] in modum ha[e]c vita[e] mea[e] quadra[n]t co[n]ditioni mihi erat ♐ 2 vel 3 gradus in Horos.
                        Hoc vel maximè me perpessu[m] esse o[mn]es noru[n]t familiares amici 
                    </marginalia_text>
                    <symbol_in_text name="Sagittarius"/>
                </position>
            </language>
            <translation>
                Wonderful in the manner [in which] these things of my life fit in my condition; it was Sagittarius, two or three degrees in the horoscope.
                This or greatly so, all my friends found out that I endured to the full.
            </translation>
